---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Crisis Services - Ossified Orbit">
	<div class="page-container">
		<h1>Crisis Services</h1>
		<div class="hero-section">
			<p>Immediate, compassionate support and intervention services available 24/7 for individuals and families facing mental health, substance use, or behavioral health crises.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="emergency-banner">
			<div class="emergency-content">
				<h2>üö® Need Immediate Help?</h2>
				<p>If you or someone you know is in immediate danger, please call 911 or go to your nearest emergency room.</p>
				<div class="crisis-contacts">
					<div class="crisis-number">
						<strong>Crisis Hotline:</strong> 1-800-CRISIS-1 (24/7)
					</div>
					<div class="crisis-number">
						<strong>Text Crisis Line:</strong> Text HOME to 741741
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="content-sections">
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>Immediate Crisis Response</h2>
				<p>Our crisis services provide immediate, professional support when mental health, substance use, or behavioral emergencies occur. Our trained crisis intervention specialists are available around the clock to provide assessment, stabilization, and connection to appropriate resources.</p>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>Crisis Services Available</h2>
				<div class="services-grid">
					<div class="service-card hotline">
						<div class="service-icon">üìû</div>
						<h3>24/7 Crisis Hotline</h3>
						<p>Immediate phone support with trained crisis counselors who can provide de-escalation, safety planning, and resource connection.</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Confidential crisis counseling</li>
							<li>Risk assessment and safety planning</li>
							<li>Resource and referral information</li>
							<li>Follow-up services coordination</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card mobile">
						<div class="service-icon">üöê</div>
						<h3>Mobile Crisis Response</h3>
						<p>Crisis specialists who come directly to you - at home, work, school, or wherever the crisis is occurring.</p>
						<ul>
							<li>On-site crisis assessment</li>
							<li>De-escalation and stabilization</li>
							<li>Safety planning with individuals and families</li>
							<li>Connection to ongoing services</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card respite">
						<div class="service-icon">üè†</div>
						<h3>Crisis Respite Services</h3>
						<p>Short-term residential services providing a safe environment for stabilization and recovery planning.</p>
						<ul>
							<li>24/7 supervised care</li>
							<li>Individual crisis counseling</li>
							<li>Medication management</li>
							<li>Discharge planning and follow-up</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card peer">
						<div class="service-icon">üë•</div>
						<h3>Peer Crisis Support</h3>
						<p>Support from individuals who have lived experience with mental health challenges and recovery.</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Lived experience perspective</li>
							<li>Hope and recovery focused</li>
							<li>Cultural and linguistic matching</li>
							<li>Ongoing peer support connections</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>Specialized Crisis Programs</h2>
				<div class="specialized-programs">
					<div class="program-card">
						<h3>Youth Crisis Services</h3>
						<p>Specialized crisis intervention for children, adolescents, and their families, including school-based crisis response.</p>
						<div class="program-features">
							<span>Ages 0-18</span>
							<span>Family-centered approach</span>
							<span>School liaison services</span>
							<span>Trauma-informed care</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="program-card">
						<h3>Adult Crisis Services</h3>
						<p>Comprehensive crisis intervention for adults experiencing mental health, substance use, or co-occurring disorders.</p>
						<div class="program-features">
							<span>18+ years</span>
							<span>Co-occurring disorders</span>
							<span>Dual diagnosis support</span>
							<span>Recovery-oriented care</span>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="program-card">
						<h3>Geriatric Crisis Services</h3>
						<p>Age-appropriate crisis services for older adults, including coordination with medical providers and family systems.</p>
						<div class="program-features">
							<span>65+ years</span>
							<span>Medical coordination</span>
							<span>Caregiver support</span>
							<span>Placement services</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>What to Expect</h2>
				<div class="process-steps">
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">1</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>Initial Contact</h3>
							<p>Call our crisis line or request mobile response. Initial screening and risk assessment completed immediately.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">2</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>Crisis Assessment</h3>
							<p>Comprehensive assessment of immediate safety needs, mental health status, and available supports.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">3</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>Intervention & Stabilization</h3>
							<p>Immediate interventions to ensure safety, reduce distress, and begin stabilization process.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">4</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>Safety Planning</h3>
							<p>Development of safety plan with individual and supports, including coping strategies and resources.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="step">
						<div class="step-number">5</div>
						<div class="step-content">
							<h3>Connection to Services</h3>
							<p>Linkage to appropriate ongoing services, follow-up appointments, and community supports.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section cta">
				<h2>Crisis Support When You Need It</h2>
				<p>Crisis situations can happen to anyone, anytime. Our team is here to provide immediate support, stabilization, and hope during the most difficult moments.</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="tel:1-800-273-8255" class="cta-button emergency">Call Crisis Line: 1-800-CRISIS-1</a>
					<a href="/contact" class="cta-button secondary">Learn More About Services</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-container {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 1200px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: #000000;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.hero-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}
	
	.hero-section p {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: #f39c12;
	}
	
	.emergency-banner {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}
	
	.emergency-content h2 {
		color: #000000;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
	}
	
	.emergency-content p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.crisis-contacts {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 2rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	
	.crisis-number {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}
	
	.content-sections {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}
	
	.service-section h2 {
		color: #f39c12;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 2rem;
	}
	
	.service-section p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.services-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	
	.service-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.service-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.2);
	}
	
	.service-icon {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	
	.service-card h3 {
		color: #e67e22;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.4rem;
	}
	
	.service-card > p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		text-align: left;
	}
	
	.service-card ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		text-align: left;
	}
	
	.service-card li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}
	
	.service-card li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}
	
	.service-card li::before {
		content: "‚úì";
		color: #f39c12;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-right: 0.5rem;
	}
	
	.specialized-programs {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	
	.program-card {
		background: rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.1);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.3);
	}
	
	.program-card h3 {
		color: #f39c12;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}
	
	.program-card p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.program-features {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}
	
	.program-features span {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 15px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #e67e22;
	}
	
	.process-steps {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	
	.step {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
	}
	
	.step-number {
		background: #f39c12;
		color: #000000;
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	.step-content h3 {
		color: #f39c12;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
	}
	
	.step-content p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	.cta {
		text-align: center;
		background: rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.1);
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.3);
	}
	
	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	
	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}
	
	.cta-button.emergency {
		background: #e74c3c;
		color: #000000;
	}
	
	.cta-button.emergency:hover {
		background: #c0392b;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	
	.cta-button.secondary {
		background: #f39c12;
		color: #000000;
	}
	
	.cta-button.secondary:hover {
		background: #e67e22;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-container {
			width: 100%;
		}
		
		h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		
		.hero-section p {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}
		
		.crisis-contacts {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
		
		.services-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		
		.specialized-programs {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		
		.step {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}
	}
</style>